'''豐胸'''是指女性設法增加[[乳房|乳房]]的大小。女性乳房在[[青春期|青春期]]或[[懷孕|懷孕]]時，因[[乳腺生長|乳腺生長]]，乳房會變大。豐胸一般是指用人工的方式進行刺激，或進行[[隆乳|隆乳]]手術使乳房變大。

乳房是女性的[[第二性徵|第二性徵]]，是女性[[性感|性吸引力]]中重要的部份，也代表其[[女性化|女性化]]的部份。因此若女性認為其乳房在某些方面有所不足，就可能會用一些方式，設法使乳房變大<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sexarchive.info/ATLAS_EN/html/secondary_characteristics.html |title=Secondary sex characteristics |publisher=.hu-berlin.de |accessdate=2011-10-31 |archive-date=2013-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130622035035/http://www.sexarchive.info/ATLAS_EN/html/secondary_characteristics.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

豐胸的方式有以下數種：
*[[隆胸|隆乳手術]]，包括植入[[乳房植體|乳房植體]]或是自體脂肪隆乳等方式。
*[[藥物|藥物]]或[[激素|荷爾蒙]]豐胸，比如服用[[雌激素|雌激素]]或{{le|豐胸補充劑|breast enlargement supplement}}<ref name="GöretzlehnerLauritzen2012">{{cite book|author1=Gunther Göretzlehner|author2=Christian Lauritzen|author3=Thomas Römer|author4=Winfried Rossmanith|title=Praktische Hormontherapie in der Gynäkologie|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=TIs2WhfYzZ4C&pg=PA385|date=1 January 2012|publisher=Walter de Gruyter|isbn=978-3-11-024568-4|pages=385–}}</ref><ref name="ManselFodstad2007">{{cite book|author1=R.E. Mansel|author2=Oystein Fodstad|author3=Wen G. Jiang|title=Metastasis of Breast Cancer|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=14pb5b6gT-oC&pg=PA217|date=14 June 2007|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=978-1-4020-5866-0|pages=217–|access-date=2020-05-29|archive-date=2016-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201061335/https://books.google.com/books?id=14pb5b6gT-oC&pg=PA217|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pmid96104252">{{cite journal|title=Hormonal breast augmentation: prognostic relevance of insulin-like growth factor-I|url=|journal=Gynecol. Endocrinol.|issue=2|doi=10.3109/09513599809024960|year=1998|volume=12|pages=123–7|pmid=9610425|vauthors=Hartmann BW, Laml T, Kirchengast S, Albrecht AE, Huber JC}}</ref>。台灣也有許多宣稱有豐胸療效的違規食品廣告<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160224/802292/ |title=食品廣告誆瘦身豐胸　女性最難抗拒 |accessdate=2016-06-18 |archive-date=2016-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506140357/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160224/802292/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>（台灣規定食品廣告不得有像「豐胸」之類改變身體外觀的文字<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://health.gov.taipei/Default.aspx?tabid=762 |title=醫療衛生法規之廣告用語規定（得列/不得列）一覽表 |accessdate=2016-06-18 |archive-date=2016-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618193012/http://health.gov.taipei/Default.aspx?tabid=762 |dead-url=no }}</ref>）。
*增加[[食物熱量|食物熱量]]的攝取以增加身體的[[脂肪組織|脂肪組織]]，此組織為乳房構造的一部份<ref>{{cite journal|title=Contribution of breast volume and weight to body fat distribution in females|url=https://deepblue.lib.umich.edu/bitstream/2027.42/37602/1/1330530113_ftp.pdf|first1=VL|last2=Campaigne|first2=B|date=July 1980|journal=Am. J. Phys. Anthropol.|issue=1|doi=10.1002/ajpa.1330530113|volume=53|pages=93–100|pmid=7416252|last3=Freedson|first3=P|last4=Sady|first4=S|last5=Katch|first5=FI|last6=Behnke|first6=AR|last1=Katch}}</ref>，多少比例的脂肪會增加到乳房因人而異，受KLF14基因所控制<ref>{{cite journal|title=Identification of an imprinted master trans regulator at the KLF14 locus related to multiple metabolic phenotypes|first1=KS|last2=Hedman|first2=AK|date=June 2011|journal=Nat. Genet.|issue=6|doi=10.1038/ng.833|volume=43|pages=561–4|pmc=3192952|pmid=21572415|last3=Grundberg|first3=E|display-authors=et al|last1=Small}}</ref>。
*機械性豐胸（Mechanical breast enhancement），比如使用[[BRAVA丰胸整形系统|BRAVA丰胸整形系统]]（BRAVA Breast Enhancement and Shaping System）<ref name="SchlenzKaider2007">{{cite journal|last1=Schlenz|first1=Ingrid|last2=Kaider|first2=Alexandra|title=The Brava External Tissue Expander: Is Breast Enlargement without Surgery a Reality?|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_plastic-and-reconstructive-surgery_2007-11_120_6/page/1680|journal=Plastic and Reconstructive Surgery|volume=120|issue=6|year=2007|pages=1680–1689|issn=0032-1052|doi=10.1097/01.prs.0000267637.43207.19}}</ref>。
*{{le|Mark Eden bust developer|Mark Eden bust developer}}，一套在1960年代及1970年代聲稱可以豐胸的設備，後來確定無效。

